com.github.katjahahn.sections

Class SectionHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.katjahahn.sections.SectionHeader

  • public class SectionHeader
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an entry of the SectionTable. The instance is usually created by the SectionTable.
